South Korea's wholesale price index, base1980, rose 0.2 pct to 125.1 in March after a 0.2 pct rise inFebruary but was 0.6 pct lower than its March 1986 level, theBank of Korea said.    The March consumer price index, same base, rose 0.5 pct to146.0 after a 0.1 pct gain in February, for a year-on-year riseof 1.7 pct. REUTER&#3;